name: Ares
overview: When her friend suffers a bizarre accident, Rosa realizes the secret student society they've just joined is built on demonic secrets from Dutch history.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Rosa, an ambitious and intelligent college student with a trying home life, is recruited to join an exclusive and mysterious society.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: As Rosa undergoes a trying and terrifying initiation ceremony, a fellow "novice" goes missing, putting the leaders of Ares on high alert.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Rosa faces dueling responsibilities while Jacob submits to an interrogation. Later, Fleur invites Rosa to a party, where fates are seemingly sealed.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: The leaders of Ares go to extremes in an effort to hide the truth behind Rosa's gruesome discovery. Meanwhile, Jacob's affliction worsens.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Arnold crosses paths with a presence from his past. Rosa has an unwelcome run-in with a rival. Jacob makes a cryptic prediction.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Fleur lashes out following a devastating loss. After Rosa takes steps to reconnect with her family, Carmen shares a shocking truth.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Maurits ponders who should become the next president of Ares, Carmen faces a sadistic test, and Rosa manages to surprise Jacob.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Carmen issues a dire warning to Rosa as things at Ares come to an explosive end and a terrible secret is finally revealed.
